    "Condition : 1 - The maximum steady brightness of the fascia sign hereby permitted is not to exceed 200 candelas per sq.m.\r\nReason: To ensure the sign does not have an adverse effect on the amenity of the area in accordance with Council policy LP9 and to comply with paragraph 132 of the National Planning Policy Framework 2021.\r\n",
