    "Condition : 3 - The illumination of the sign(s) hereby permitted shall be by static illumination only. \r\nReason: In the interest of highway safety and of the visual amenities of the locality in accordance with Council policy LP9 and to comply with paragraph 132 of the National Planning Policy Framework 2021.\r\n"
